      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - Applicant must be a family member of a prisoner currently serving sentence in a state jail in Gujarat.\n  - The prisoner should be the sole or main earner of the family.\n  - The prisoner&amp;#39;s family must be economically dependent on the prisoner.\n  - The total family income should not exceed ₹1,50,000/- per annum.\n  - The family should not be fragmented (i.e., should be living together and dependent on the prisoner).\n\n<br>\n\n",
